quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  37,77,"Min mb…ói gelngol makko ngol, heddotoo…ďe …ďen."
  37,78,"Min ngaccani mo mantoore, e sakkitii…ďe …ďeen."
  37,79,"Kisal wonii e Nuuhu, e ndeer winndere nden."
  37,80,"Ko non woni ko Min mbarjorta mo∆ī∆īim…ďe …ďen."
  37,81,"KaŇčko, ko o jeyanoo…óo e jiyaa…ďe Amen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  37,82,"Refti Min njooli heddii …ďe …ďeen."
  37,83,"Hino jeyanoo e jokkunoo…ďe mo …ďe Ibraahiima."
  37,84,"Tuma nde ardunoo e Joomi makko, e …ďernde hisnde."
  37,85,"Nde o maakannoo ben makko e yim…ďe mum …ďeen: "Ko hol…óum ndewoton?"
  37,86,"E ko dewetee…ói pefindaa…ói, ko wanaa Alla, paala…óon?"
  37,87,"Ko cikku…óon e Joomiraawo tagoore ngon?""
  37,88,"O ndaariri ndaarande to koode,"
  37,89,"o maaki: "Ko mi √Īawn…óo"."
  37,90,"∆Āe ngacci mo, …ďe nduŇčti."
  37,91,"O mooltii e dewetee…ói ma…ď…ďe …óin, o maaki: "E on √Īaamataa?"
  37,92,"Ko he…ďi on, on kaalataa?""
  37,93,"O naatnani, fiyirde …ói √Īaamo ngon."
  37,94,"∆Āe peewti e makko, hi…ďe njaawno."
  37,95,"O maaki: "E on ndeway ko lesu…óon!,ceh…óon)."
  37,96,"hara le ko Alla tagi on, e ko ngolloton?""
  37,97,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Mahanee mo mahdi, mbugo…óon mo ka dul…ďayange"."
  37,98,"∆Āe pa'andanii mo feere; kono Min mb…ói …ďe sooybe …ďen."
  37,99,"O maaki: "Min on, ko mi peroowo ka Joomi am, aray nde O feewnata kam."
  37,100,"Joomi am, wee…óam ge…óal mo∆ī∆īu…ďe"."
  37,101,"Min mbeltiniri mo, ge…óal mu√Ī√Īii…óo."
  37,102,"Nde on yottinoo e makko jahal, [Ibraahiima] maaki: "Ko an …ďi…ó…óo am, min mi yi'ii e …óoyngol, won'de mi…óo hirse. Ndaaru ko yi'i…óaa". [Ismaa'iila] maaki: "eey ma baaba'en, mba…óee ko njamira…óon kon, on tawoyay kam, si Alla ja…ďii, jiyaa…óo e mu√Īii…ďe …ďen"."